{"tid":1130124,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"2019韓國福布斯名人榜出爐 BLACKPINK&BTS","createTime":"2019-04-28T22:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T13:16:13.000Z","uid":250919,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff194fd4c979c16fff8348aaaa12ffc39da2d7c","tid":1130124,"uid":250919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T22:52:40.000Z","msg":"2019韓國福布斯名人榜昨日正式公佈<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK首奪一位，BTS今年則獲第二位，緊接是男團WANNAONE。<br />\n<br />\n順位如下（附有翻譯）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcskaho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpcskaho.png&h=8101058e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報BLACKPINK四名成員在Instagram的跟蹤人數不斷倍增，Twitter等社交媒體數字都相當驚人，特別是在美國、海外人氣極高，早前登上Late show with James Corden一集更令節目首度榮獲該週全美最受歡迎Variety Show類別<br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團隨著新專輯突破數百萬張新紀錄，更邀請當紅歌手Halsey錄製新曲，令人氣持續高企，收入、新聞更是包辦一位"},{"pid":"47f0d989cbb35594616e56285b021b6b52e4ea4e","tid":1130124,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"樓主你走先 呢到我頂住"},{"pid":"b8019ff6e0328c008766e6ac5a0f57a361921ac6","tid":1130124,"uid":124156,"like":17,"dislike":13,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"Bp 會勁過bts?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n造假造到咁出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f7ec8b19c8fbf223fd885bb332b8779fc197d4","tid":1130124,"uid":201565,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b8019ff6e0328c008766e6ac5a0f57a361921ac6","tid":1130124,"uid":124156,"like":17,"dislike":13,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"Bp 會勁過bts?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i